# Kali Linux – Technical Evaluation

## Overview
Kali Linux is a Debian-based distribution focused on cybersecurity, penetration testing, and digital forensics.

## Installation Experience
- Smooth installation with guided partitioning.
- Default tools preinstalled, reducing setup time.

## Strengths
- Includes industry-standard security tools.
- Stable Debian base.
- Strong community documentation.

## Limitations
- Heavy for older hardware.
- Not recommended for general-purpose desktop use.

## Best Use Cases
✓ Ethical hacking  
✓ Security audits  
✓ Vulnerability assessments  
✓ CTF practice

